						               													<description>Recruit Companions, Learn Knowledge, and take Action to create a unique and formidable Guild capable of battling back ferocious creatures to reclaim the Kingdom!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;GuildCraft is a deckbuilding, tableau-building fantasy sandbox game for 2-4 Players. Set in a Medieval Fantasy setting, each Player controls a Guild that they will build up and customize over the course of the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players are tasked with a mission from the King to go forth into the world to conquer and claim new territory for the Kingdom.  Beware though, the lands beyond the Castle grounds are crawling with dangerous, ferocious creatures, intent on cutting down anyone who encroaches into their domains.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During their Turn, Players will play and use Cards to venture forth and discover new lands, Gather valuable Resources, and eliminate the deadly Creatures that plague the Kingdom.  The Resources that they Gather can be used to Hire helpful Companions, Learn  Knowledge, or Develop powerful Actions to aid them in their Quest.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Player with the greatest Guild at the End Game is the victor!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
